name: Forward!
description: I discovered the wonderful artist @yankovskaya, was amazed by her paintings and decided to make such a composition. For a long time I could not complete the picture. Only the contest from @yankovskaya made it possible to put the final point, to complete the central element of the composition. The title of the picture speaks for itself. I share Belkovsky's concept of an impending new matriarchy, I lacked an inspiring impulse that would help me materialize my feelings. The creation of the elements of the composition was inspired by the great artist Deineka.
